body:
It would be nice to escape single/double quotes inside selected text when quoting it
This is applicable for most programming languages

Here is c# use case:
1. Create c# file. 
```c#
public class Program {
    public static void Main() {
        Console.WriteLine("Test");
    }
}
```
3. Select text in quotes including surrounding quotes
4. Press " (double quote) on keyboard

I would expect inner quotes to be escaped to look like below
```c#
        Console.WriteLine("\"Test"\");
```
